<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Kivo — PDV, estoque, financeiro e mesas num só sistema</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Kivo: sistema completo para comércio e food service. PDV rápido, gestão de estoque, compras inteligentes, DRE, caixa, mesas, cardápio online. Funciona offline e salva na nuvem. Teste grátis por 15 dias." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/logo_kivo-icon.svg" />
  <%- include('partials/theme-init') %>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f2f0f1;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --surface-hover: #f8f7f8;
      --border: #d4d4d8;
      --border-light: #eae8ea;
      --text: #1e1e2a;
      --muted: #8a8a98;
      --primary: #FF8000;
      --primary-hover: #ff9225;
      --primary-soft: color-mix(in srgb, #FF8000 10%, transparent);
      --danger: #ef4444;
      --danger-soft: #fce4ec;
      --success: #16a34a;
      --success-soft: #d1fae5;
      --warning: #b45309;
      --warning-soft: #fef3e0;
      --radius: 10px;
      --shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
      --shadow-lg: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
      --glass-bg: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      --glass-bg-strong: rgba(255,255,255,.86);
      --glass-border: rgba(255,255,255,.7);
      --glass-ring: rgba(11,11,11,.07);
      --glass-blur: 18px;
      --glass-sheen: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.55) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 60%);
      --overlay: rgba(20, 22, 35, 0.45);
      --accent-blue: #3b82f6;
    }
    :root[data-theme="dark"] {
      --bg: #14161c;
      --surface: #1c1f26;
      --surface-hover: #262a33;
      --border: #383c46;
      --border-light: #2a2d36;
      --text: #ececf0;
      --muted: #8a8a97;
      --primary: #FF8000;
      --primary-hover: #ff9225;
      --primary-soft: color-mix(in srgb, #FF8000 18%, transparent);
      --danger: #ff6b6b;
      --danger-soft: color-mix(in srgb, #ff6b6b 18%, transparent);
      --success: #4ade80;
      --success-soft: color-mix(in srgb, #4ade80 18%, transparent);
      --warning: #fbbf24;
      --warning-soft: color-mix(in srgb, #fbbf24 20%, transparent);
      --shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
      --shadow-lg: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
      --glass-bg: rgba(32,36,45,.72);
      --glass-bg-strong: rgba(32,36,45,.88);
      --glass-border: rgba(255,255,255,.09);
      --glass-ring: rgba(0,0,0,.5);
      --glass-blur: 18px;
      --glass-sheen: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.07) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 60%);
      --overlay: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
      --accent-blue: #60a5fa;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;
    }
    body::before {
      content: ""; position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: -1; pointer-events: none;
      background:
        radial-gradient(760px circle at 8% -6%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 16%, transparent), transparent 62%),
        radial-gradient(680px circle at 96% 4%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-blue) 12%, transparent), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(720px circle at 62% 108%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 9%, transparent), transparent 60%);
    }
    a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; }
    .wrap { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.25rem; }

    /* ─── Topbar ─── */
    .topbar {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
      background: var(--glass-bg); backdrop-filter: blur(18px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    }
    .topbar-in { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; height: 64px; }
    .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .6rem; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text); }
    .brand img { height: 34px; }
    .nav { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; margin-left: auto; align-items: center; }
    .nav a { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; font-size: .95rem; }
    .nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .nav { gap: .75rem; }
      .nav a:not(.btn) { display: none; }
      .brand img { height: 28px; }
    }
    .theme-btn {
      background: none; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted);
      border-radius: 999px; width: 36px; height: 36px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1rem;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; font-weight: 700;
      background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      padding: .7rem 1.3rem; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 35%, transparent);
      transition: transform .12s, background .15s;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: var(--primary-hover); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn.secondary {
      background: var(--surface); color: var(--text); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); box-shadow: none;
    }
    .btn.big { padding: .95rem 1.9rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }

    /* ─── Hero ─── */
    .hero { padding: 4.5rem 0 2.5rem; text-align: center; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem); line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; letter-spacing: -.02em; }
    .hero h1 em { color: var(--primary); font-style: normal; }
    .hero p.sub { font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.3rem); color: var(--muted); max-width: 46rem; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .hero-note { color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; }
    .chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .6rem; justify-content: center; margin: 2rem 0 3rem; }
    .chip {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: 999px;
      padding: .4rem 1rem; font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow); display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .45rem;
    }
    .chip svg { color: var(--primary); flex: none; }

    .shot-frame {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); overflow: hidden; position: relative;
    }
    .shot-frame .bar {
      display: flex; gap: .4rem; padding: .65rem .9rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 70%, var(--bg));
    }
    .shot-frame .bar i { width: 11px; height: 11px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--border); display: block; }
    .shot-frame .bar i:nth-child(1) { background: #ff5f57; } .shot-frame .bar i:nth-child(2) { background: #febc2e; } .shot-frame .bar i:nth-child(3) { background: #28c840; }
    .shot-frame img { display: block; width: 100%; }
    :root[data-theme="dark"] .theme-swap .shot-light { display: none; }
    :root:not([data-theme="dark"]) .theme-swap .shot-dark { display: none; }
    :root[data-theme="dark"] .logo-light { display: none; }
    :root:not([data-theme="dark"]) .logo-dark { display: none; }

    /* ─── Seções de recurso ─── */
    section { padding: 3.5rem 0; }
    .kicker { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: .8rem; letter-spacing: .12em; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.2vw, 2.2rem); line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 .75rem; letter-spacing: -.01em; }
    .feature { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.25fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4.5rem; }
    .feature:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .feature.flip .feat-text { order: 2; }
    .feature p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .feature ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1.25rem 0 0; display: grid; gap: .6rem; }
    .feature li { display: flex; gap: .6rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: .98rem; }
    .feature li svg { color: var(--primary); flex: none; margin-top: .25rem; }
    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .feature { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
      .feature.flip .feat-text { order: 0; }
    }

    /* ─── Cardápio (mockup celular) ─── */
    .menu-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; }
    @media (max-width: 860px) { .menu-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .phone {
      width: min(320px, 86vw); margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 42px; padding: .8rem;
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }
    .phone-screen { border-radius: 32px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border-light); background: var(--bg); }
    .phone-head { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; padding: 1.4rem 1.1rem 1rem; }
    .phone-head .rest { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .phone-head .status { font-size: .75rem; opacity: .9; }
    .phone-cats { display: flex; gap: .4rem; padding: .7rem .9rem 0; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .phone-cats span { font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; padding: .25rem .7rem; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); color: var(--muted); }
    .phone-cats span.on { background: var(--primary); border-color: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
    .menu-item { display: flex; gap: .7rem; align-items: center; padding: .7rem .9rem; }
    .menu-item + .menu-item { border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light); }
    .menu-item img { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 12px; object-fit: cover; flex: none; }
    .menu-item .n { font-weight: 700; font-size: .84rem; line-height: 1.25; }
    .menu-item .d { color: var(--muted); font-size: .72rem; }
    .menu-item .p { margin-left: auto; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); font-size: .84rem; white-space: nowrap; }

    /* ─── Grid de destaques ─── */
    .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .card {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.5rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .card .ico {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--primary-soft);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: .9rem;
    }
    .card h3 { margin: 0 0 .4rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: .92rem; }

    /* ─── Planos ─── */
    .plans { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(230px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .plan {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1.5px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow); display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    }
    .plan.featured { border-color: var(--primary); position: relative; }
    .plan.featured::before {
      content: "Mais escolhido"; position: absolute; top: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: var(--primary); color: #fff; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 800;
      padding: .2rem .8rem; border-radius: 999px; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .plan h3 { margin: 0 0 .25rem; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .plan .tag { color: var(--muted); font-size: .85rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .plan ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; display: grid; gap: .5rem; flex: 1; }
    .plan li { display: flex; gap: .5rem; font-size: .9rem; align-items: flex-start; }
    .plan li svg { flex: none; margin-top: .3rem; }
    .plan li.yes svg { color: var(--primary); }
    .plan li.no { color: var(--muted); }
    .plan li.no svg { color: var(--border); }
    .plan .btn { justify-content: center; }

    /* ─── FAQ ─── */
    .faq { max-width: 46rem; margin: 2rem auto 0; }
    .faq details {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .faq summary { font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; }
    .faq details p { color: var(--muted); margin: .75rem 0 0; }

    /* ─── CTA final ─── */
    .cta-final {
      text-align: center; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
      border-radius: 22px; padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-final::before {
      content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
      background: radial-gradient(600px circle at 50% -20%, var(--primary-soft), transparent 70%);
    }
    /* ─── Formulário de contato ─── */
    .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; margin-top: 3rem; }
    @media (max-width: 860px) { .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; } }
    .form-card {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.75rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }
    .form-card label { display: block; font-weight: 700; font-size: .88rem; margin: 0 0 .3rem; }
    .form-card .req { color: var(--primary); }
    .form-field { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .form-card input, .form-card textarea {
      width: 100%; padding: .7rem .9rem; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 1rem;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg); color: var(--text);
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .form-card input:focus, .form-card textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); }
    .form-card textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 90px; }
    .form-msg { margin-top: .9rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: .95rem; display: none; }
    .form-msg.err { color: var(--danger); display: block; }
    .form-msg.ok { color: var(--primary); display: block; }
    .hp-field { position: absolute; left: -9999px; opacity: 0; height: 0; overflow: hidden; }

    footer { padding: 2.5rem 0 3rem; color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; }
    .foot-in { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light); padding-top: 1.75rem; }
    .center { text-align: center; }
    .center h2 { margin-bottom: .5rem; }
    .center > p { color: var(--muted); max-width: 44rem; margin: 0 auto; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="wrap topbar-in">
      <a class="brand" href="/">
        <img class="logo-light" src="/img/landing/logo_kivo-horizontal.svg" alt="Kivo" />
        <img class="logo-dark" src="/img/landing/logo_kivo-horizontal_branco.svg" alt="Kivo" />
      </a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="#recursos">Recursos</a>
        <a href="#planos">Planos</a>
        <a href="/wiki">Wiki</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <button class="theme-btn" onclick="toggleTheme()" title="Alternar tema" aria-label="Alternar tema claro/escuro">◐</button>
        <a class="btn" href="<%= downloadUrl %>">
          <svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
          Baixar grátis
        </a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ─── HERO ─── -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>O sistema completo para<br /><em>vender, controlar e crescer</em></h1>
      <p class="sub">
        PDV rápido, estoque inteligente, financeiro, mesas e cardápio online — tudo num só lugar.
        Funciona <strong>sem internet</strong> e, quando conectado, salva tudo automaticamente na nuvem.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a class="btn big" href="<%= downloadUrl %>">
          <svg width="19" height="19" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
          Baixar para Windows — v<%= appVersion %>
        </a>
        <a class="btn big secondary" href="#recursos">Conhecer os recursos</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-note">✔ 15 dias grátis, sem cartão de crédito &nbsp;·&nbsp; ✔ Migração de dados inclusa</div>

      <div class="chips">
        <span class="chip"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Funciona 100% offline</span>
        <span class="chip"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Nuvem automática</span>
        <span class="chip"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Treinamento e suporte 24/7</span>
        <span class="chip"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Wiki bem documentada</span>
      </div>

      <div class="shot-frame theme-swap">
        <div class="bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
        <img class="shot-light" src="/img/landing/pdv.png" alt="PDV do Kivo com carrinho de venda montado" />
        <img class="shot-dark" src="/img/landing/pdv-dark.png" alt="PDV do Kivo no tema escuro" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── RECURSOS ─── -->
  <section id="recursos">
    <div class="wrap">

      <div class="center" style="margin-bottom:3.5rem">
        <div class="kicker">Recursos</div>
        <h2>Tudo o que o seu negócio precisa, de verdade</h2>
        <p>Telas reais do sistema, sem maquiagem: é assim que o Kivo funciona no dia a dia do seu balcão, da sua cozinha e do seu escritório.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feat-text">
          <div class="kicker">PDV</div>
          <h2>Frente de caixa veloz, feita para o balcão</h2>
          <p>Bipe o código de barras ou busque pelo nome. Atalhos de teclado para tudo — finalizar, desconto, acréscimo, imprimir — e várias vendas abertas ao mesmo tempo.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Dinheiro, PIX, débito, crédito e venda a prazo</li>
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Complementos e adicionais direto no carrinho</li>
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Preço por cliente, listas de preço e fidelidade</li>
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Continua vendendo mesmo se a internet cair</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="shot-frame theme-swap">
          <div class="bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
          <img class="shot-light" loading="lazy" src="/img/landing/pdv.png" alt="PDV do Kivo" />
          <img class="shot-dark" loading="lazy" src="/img/landing/pdv-dark.png" alt="PDV do Kivo no tema escuro" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature flip">
        <div class="feat-text">
          <div class="kicker">Catálogo</div>
          <h2>Cadastro de produtos com todos os tipos</h2>
          <p>Produto simples, kit, combo, fracionado, produzido com ficha técnica, serviço, variantes e complementos. Importação e exportação por planilha.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> <strong>Sugestor de imagens inteligente:</strong> cadastrou "Coca-Cola"? A foto certa aparece sozinha</li>
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Cadastro rápido bipando o código de barras</li>
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Ficha técnica desconta insumos do estoque a cada venda</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="shot-frame">
          <div class="bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
          <img loading="lazy" src="/img/landing/produtos.png" alt="Cadastro de produtos do Kivo com fotos, preços, custos e estoque" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feat-text">
          <div class="kicker">Compras &amp; Estoque</div>
